{"tid":1797150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一間你打死都唔會幫襯既黃店","createTime":"2019-12-25T07:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T01:39:34.000Z","uid":235746,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2b6de0f8dda7529fbfe594e897c1678827d35469","tid":1797150,"uid":235746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T07:41:28.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">深水埗福利模型</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母條撚樣福姑同d員工平時串柒柒<br />\nd嘢又唔撚係平過人 一班垃圾熟客成日吹捧<br />\n有嘢炒起就平人幾十蚊 實則得幾隻 <br />\n等人以為佢係良心店 唔炒埋一份<br />\n隔一排就會攞出黎賣炒價<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傻閪福姑仲要成日呻吟話自己無錢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n理撚得你黃過我條底褲<br />\n反正我呢世都唔會再幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e23c1030ac520384a6914f4c10c522b4f3c0632","tid":1797150,"uid":203710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T07:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2L7iThb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2L7iThb.jpg&h=b693c9ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43fc0a66af9e81f993c198f5f94a83fad7c8f158","tid":1797150,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T07:43:09.000Z","msg":"借個位嚟推廣<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂廁</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊將洗手間變成實體連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1796473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1796473</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"34a8f544ccdcdec4c5b89e2c6eabd3172040e6c2","tid":1797150,"uid":235746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e23c1030ac520384a6914f4c10c522b4f3c0632","tid":1797150,"uid":203710,